      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――リズノワの沖縄合宿、当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――LizNoir's Okinawa Camp",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-03.m4a",
          "delay": 4233.3333333,
          "startTime": 4.2333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5566.6666667,
          "startTime": 5.5666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ここがみんなが泊まっているホテルか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ this is the hotel where everyone is staying…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ryokan-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 5.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_02-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "こころ達の部屋は隣なので\n気付かれないように気をつけて下さいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kokoro and the others' room is next door‚\nso be careful not to be noticed.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、気をつけるよ\nそれにしてもこのホテル、なんだか随分ボロいな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ I'll be careful.\nBy the way‚ this hotel looks quite run-down…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ryokan-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 16.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "建物は老朽化が酷いし、海からも遠い……\nどうして合宿先にこんな寂れたホテルを選んだんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The building is in terrible condition‚ and it's far from the beach…\nWhy did you choose such a shabby hotel for the camp?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ryokan-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 24.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_02-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "選んだ訳じゃないです～\n予算がなくて格安ホテルしか泊まれなかっただけです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I didn't choose it~\nWe didn't have enough budget‚ so we could only afford a cheap hotel.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "予算なら事務所から十分出ていたはずだろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But there should have been enough budget from the agency‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ryokan-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 34.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_02-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "それが、飛行機のチケットを手配して\n旅先で使いそうな物を買い揃えて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I used the budget to arrange flight tickets‚\nbuy things we might need during the trip…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_02-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "海で遊ぶアクティビティを予約しまくったら\nお金がなくなっちゃいましたぁ。てへっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I also made a lot of reservations for beach activities‚\nand then… the money ran out. Teehee~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ryokan-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 48.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "こころのプランがずさん過ぎて\n安宿に泊まることになったのか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Your plan was too sloppy‚\nand that's why we ended up staying in a cheap hostel…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_02-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "確かに予算はほとんど残ってませんけど\n旅の計画はばっちりですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's true that there's almost no budget left‚\nbut my travel plan is perfect!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ryokan-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 59.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_02-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "こころのパーフェクトなプランに\nきっと莉央さんは感激の涙を流して喜びますよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio-san will definitely\nbe moved to tears by Kokoro's perfect plan~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ryokan-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 66.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_02-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "だから大船に乗ったつもりで見てて下さい\nリズノワの夏合宿は大成功間違いなしです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ please watch as if we're on a big adventure!\nLizNoir's summer training camp will be a huge success‚ I guarantee it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-call-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7666.666666699995,
          "startTime": 73.9666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 10866.666666699999,
          "startTime": 77.1666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ryokan-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 74.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_02-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "……あれ？　愛ちゃんからですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Huh? It's a call from Ai-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ryokan-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 80.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_02-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "もしも～し……え！？　ホテルの設備がボロ過ぎて\n莉央さんが怒ってる？　わ、分かった、すぐ戻るね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hello… Eh!? Rio-san is angry because the hotel facilities are too shabby?\nO-Okay‚ got it. I'll be right back!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.5666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9433.3333334,
          "startTime": 87.7666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ryokan-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 89.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_02-kkr010.m4a",
      "text": "緊急事態なのでみんなの所に戻りますね\n{user}さんは部屋から出ないで下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's an emergency‚ so I'll go back to everyone's room.\n{user}-san‚ don't leave your room.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_02-kkr011.m4a",
      "text": "壁が薄いんですから\n絶対に大声を出さないで下さいね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The walls are thin‚ you know?\nAbsolutely don't raise your voice!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ryokan-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 101.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "そう言うこころの声が一番大きい気がするんだが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I feel like Kokoro's voice is the loudest…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ryokan-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 105.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_02-kkr012.m4a",
      "text": "しーっ、静かにして下さい\n動かないで、物音を立てないで、息もしないで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shhh‚ be quiet.\nDon't move‚ don't make any noise‚ don't even breathe.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ryokan-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 112.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_02-kkr013.m4a",
      "text": "そのまま息を止めてて下さいね～、それじゃ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just hold your breath‚ okay? Well then~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.3333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3200.0000000000027,
          "startTime": 115.5333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ryokan-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 118.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "う……いつまで息を止めていればいいんだ……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh… How long do I have to hold my breath…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――しばらく経ち",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――After a while",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 125.5
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 125.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ホテルから随分と離れた所まで移動したな……\nこころ達はこの辺りにいるはずだが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We've moved quite far from the hotel…\nKokoro and the others should be around here…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 133.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_02-kkr014.m4a",
      "text": "海にスーツで来るなんて変わった趣味ですね～\n暑苦しいですー。ここで何してるんですか？",
      "translations": {
