      "text": "俺を今までどう思っていたんだよ……\n……そういえば、今夜の食事はどうするつもりなんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What have you been thinking of me until now…\n…By the way‚ what are you planning to do for dinner tonight?",
        "id": ""
