      "text": "キャンプ場で食材が売ってるので\nそれを買ってみんなで料理しようかなって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The camping site has ingredients for sale‚\nso I thought we could buy them and cook together…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 300.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
