      "text": "あっ、そういえば財布がないんでした\nこれじゃ買えないですね～、どうしましょう……ちらっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ but‚ I don't have my wallet.\nI can't buy anything… sneak glances",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 308,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
