      "text": "仕方ないな。お金は立て替えておくよ\nそのかわり料理が出来たら俺にも分けてくれないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I guess we have no choice. I'll pay for it in advance.\nIn return‚ can you share the meal with me if you manage to cook something?",
        "id": ""
