      "text": "普段から自炊してる料理上手な莉央さん\nああ見えて実はお菓子作りが得意な葵さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio-san is skilled in cooking because she usually cooks for herself.\nAoi-san is surprisingly good at making sweets.",
